<div>

<br /> <br />
A Empty text box <br />
syntax : &ltinput type="text" /&gt <br />
output : <input type="text" />
<br /> <br />
A text box with populated value <br />
syntax : &ltinput type="text" value="Chetan"/&gt <br />
output : <input type="text" value="Chetan"/>
<br /><br />
A text box with place holder value<br />
syntax : &ltinput type="text" placeholder="Chetan"/&gt <br />
output : <input type="text" placeholder="Chetan"/>

<br /><br />
A text box for email with place holder value<br />
syntax : &ltinput type="text" placeholder="Chetan"/&gt <br />
output : <input type="email" placeholder="chetan_das@yahoo.com"/>
<br /><br />

A text box for password<br />
syntax : &ltinput type="text" placeholder="Chetan"/&gt <br />
output : <input type="password"/>
<br /><br />

<h3> TEXTAREA </h3>
A Empty text area <br />
syntax : &lttextarea&gt &lt/textarae&gt <br /><br />
output : <textarea> </textarea> <br /> <br />

A text area with populated text<br />
syntax : &lttextarea&gt write your comment &lt/textarae&gt <br /><br />
output : <textarea> write your comment </textarea> <br /> <br />

<br />
<h3> DROPDOWN </h3>

syntax : <br />
&ltselect&gt<br />
&nbsp&nbsp&ltoption&gt select one option &lt/option&gt<br />
&nbsp&nbsp&ltoption&gt India &lt/option&gt<br />
&nbsp&nbsp&ltoption&gt USA &lt/option&gt<br />
&nbsp&nbsp&ltoption&gt UK &lt/option&gt<br />
&lt/select&gt
<br /><br />
output: <br />
<select>
	<option> select one option </option>
	<option> India </option>
	<option> USA </option>
	<option> UK </option>
</select>
<br /><br />

<h3> CHECKBOX </h3>

syntax :<br /> 
&ltinput type="checkbox"/&gt dog<br />
&ltinput type="checkbox"/&gt cat<br />
&ltinput type="checkbox"/&gt fish<br />
&ltinput type="checkbox"/&gt cow<br />
<br />
output : <br />
<input type="checkbox"/> dog<br />
<input type="checkbox"/> cat<br />
<input type="checkbox"/> fish<br />
<input type="checkbox"/> cow<br />
<br />

<h3> RADIO BUTTON </h3>
without group i.e all radio button selectable<br /><br />
syntax : <br />
&ltinput type="radio"/&gt married<br />
&ltinput type="radio"/&gt unmarried<br /><br />
output : <br />
<input type="radio"/> married<br />
<input type="radio"/> unmarried<br />

<br />
with group i.e only one button clickable<br /><br />
syntax : <br />
&ltinput type="radio" name="status"/&gt married<br />
&ltinput type="radio" name="status"/&gt unmarried<br /><br />
output : <br />
<input type="radio" name="status"/> married<br />
<input type="radio" name="status"/> unmarried<br />
<br />
<h3> SUBMIT BUTTON </h3>

syntax : &ltinput type="submit" /&gt<br />
output : <input type="submit" /><br />

<br />Submit with customized click button <br />
syntax : &ltinput type="submit" value="clicl me!"/&gt<br />
output : <input type="submit" value="clicl me!" /><br />

<br /> As we have not assigned any name and/or value to the input parameter so on pressing<br />
button there is no effetct check out form2.html for some advance form design 

</div>
</body>
</html>
